The technician used these materials: {{materials}}

Available team products: {{products}}

Output ONLY a JSON array of matching product hash IDs. Example: ["abc123","def456"]. If no product matches, output []. Do NOT include any other text.

The technician worked {{hours}} hours.

Available team services: {{services}}

Output ONLY a JSON array of matching service hash IDs for the hours worked. Example: ["abc123","def456"]. If no service matches or no hourly rate is configured, output []. Do NOT include any other text.
